- Malzeme 1
- Malzeme 2

## Baski Ayarlari
- Dolgu: %20
- Destek: Gerekli

## Notlar
Dikkat edilmesi gerekenler..."
              rows="12"
              minlength="20"
              maxlength="10000"
              required
            ></textarea>
            <span class="char-hint"><span id="contentCount">0</span>/10000</span>
            <div class="markdown-hint">
              <span>üí° Markdown desteklenir:</span>
              <code>**kalin**</code>
              <code>*italik*</code>
              <code>## Baslik</code>
              <code>- Liste</code>
              <code>[Link](url)</code>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-actions">
            <a href="/topluluk/projeler" class="btn btn-secondary">Iptal</a>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="submitBtn">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
              Projeyi Paylas
